    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This weighty brass disk is inscribed with the ancestral names of its previous owners and now includes your own. When worn, it rests against your chest with a heavy warmth, a reminder of the strength of those who came before you. While worn and invested, you gain a +2 item bonus to Will saves. This bonus increases to +3 if the effect has the fear trait.",
